DTSTAMP:20260317T070143Z
DTSTART:20260318T130000Z
DESCRIPTION:Bar Stories Legacy Project\\\, hosted in Seattle by Nick Vega a
	nd Rebecca Lambert\\\, is coming to the GSC. Featuring your stories – brou
	ght to life! The show offers three participation options: Featured Storyte
	llers with 7-8 minute slots\\\, On-the-Fly Storytellers with 3-minute tale
	s\\\, and In-Your-Seat one-minute stories. Each story captures authentic\\
	\, real-life moments—hilarious\\\, dramatic\\\, or touching—shared in a co
	nversational style. After each tale\\\, the audience engages in a brief Q&
	A. The only rule is kindness and respect. As a bonus\\\, every storyteller
	 receives a free professional recording of their performance. Pull up a ch
	air and share your story—it’s waiting to be told! RSVP: 206.297.0875.\n\nh
	ttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/bar-stories-legacy/\n\nFrom Phinney Nei
